%% seq_11_platform_support_overview.mmd
%% Scope: Platform support interaction overview.
%% Detail files:
%%   - seq_11_notification_center.mmd
%%   - seq_12_user_settings_preferences.mmd
%%   - seq_13_system_admin_console.mmd

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    actor A as System Admin
    participant UI as Browser
    participant C as Controllers
    participant App as Commands / Queries

    Note over U,App: NOTIFICATION CENTER
    U->>UI: Open notifications / mutate read state
    UI->>C: GET/POST/DELETE /notifications/*
    C->>App: Notification actions
    C-->>UI: Inertia/JSON response

    Note over U,App: SETTINGS PREFERENCES
    U->>UI: Open/update settings
    UI->>C: GET/POST /settings/*
    C->>App: Settings actions + profile command
    C-->>UI: Redirect/render updated state

    Note over A,App: SYSTEM ADMIN CONSOLE
    A->>UI: Toggle/admin dashboard/moderation
    UI->>C: /admin/* routes
    C->>App: Admin commands/queries
    C-->>UI: Render admin pages + mutation feedback
